          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Shell Company Abuse Act</b></p> <p>This bill amends the federal criminal code to make it unlawful to establish or use a corporation, company, or other entity with the intent to conceal an election contribution or donation by a foreign national.</p> <p>A violator is subject to a criminal penalty&#8212;a fine, a prison term of up to five years, or both.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2018-05-23T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in Senate</name>
        </item>
